responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "051B65C14CECB43945913BBDF01DD734", "Great was he within the ring. A horned gladiator supreme. - Bashing skulls into mud the angry bull relished the blood. - Sing aloud all sons of the horn. Sing aloud the Bull and his scorn. - Crimson streaks painted the walls. The arena masters took a big fall. - War did arise among the half born race. Seeded by hate unable to trace. ")
name: MIDD_0017_TLS_Tablet_TheBalladOfTheBull_9
